>440(1100</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span>×（<span>12000</span>÷<span>30000</span>）<span>)</span></span></span></span></p></td><td width=\"27%\" style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 27.88%; padding-right: 5.4pt; height: 13.4pt; border-top: medium none; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\"><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 20pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span>550(1100</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span>×（<span>15000</span>÷<span>30000</span>）<span>)</span></span></span></span></p></td><td width=\"26%\" style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 26.1%; padding-right: 5.4pt; height: 13.4pt; border-top: medium none; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\"><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 20pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span>110(1100</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span>×（<span>3000</span>÷<span>30000</span>）<span>)</span></span></span></span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 4.95pt\"><td width=\"18%\" style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 18.14%; padding-right: 5.4pt; height: 4.95pt; border-top: medium none; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\"><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 20pt\"><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span>应纳税所得额调整</span></span></span></p></td><td width=\"27%\" style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: medium none; padding-bottom: 0cm; padding-left: